-- MOVES-EY names Scott Mackay as partner in national tax department
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 10:28AM EDT
-- None



Sept 16 (Reuters) - Auditing firm Ernst & Young LLP [ERNY.UL] named Scott Mackay as a partner in its national tax department in Washington DC.

Mackay previously worked as a taxation specialist with the U.S. Department of the Treasury's Office of Tax Policy.